230
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:17,850
for a view.

231
00:13:17,850 --> 00:13:21,420
And the advantage that we get because of that is that

232
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:25,620
a view will be strongly typed to one model.

233
00:13:25,620 --> 00:13:26,670
And because of that

234
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:31,530
view models are also known as strongly typed views.

235
00:13:31,530 --> 00:13:35,400
So if someone will ask you what is a strongly typed view,

236
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:37,200
that basically means that there is

237
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:41,430
a model that is specific for that view, because of that,

238
00:13:41,430 --> 00:13:45,453
because of that the view is strongly typed to a model.

239
00:13:46,530 --> 00:13:50,043
So it is always good to remember that term as well.

